Cell["\<\
Disjoint contributions for each Nambu component of the one-body potential at \
first order are 12 in total. These are distributed as follows:
i) 2 Bogoliubov diagrams dressed in the antidiagonal;
ii) 2 Bogoliubov diagrams dressed in the diagonal;
iii) 2 Exchange diagrams dressed in the propagator above;
iv) 2 Exchange diagrams dressed in the propagator below;
v) 2 Direct diagrams dressed in the left propagator;
vi) 2 Direct diagrams dressed in the right propagator;\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8746447846491413`*^9, 3.874644822571206*^9}, {
